latestIgtvVideos.title: ‼️How to Remove Body and Facial Hair‼️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The only product I use to remove my body and facial hair is “Epilator” apart from eyebrows.
This one is from @philips and you can easily find it on @amazondotin 
The cost of this one was under Rs 2000/- when I bought it.
It is travel friendly, pocket friendly and yet save time too! 
This is #NotAnAd 
I am using it since 4 years now and trust me guys this works beautifully.
Leaving my skin absolutely smooth more than I could ever imagine with wax. This is definitely a must try one ☝️ If you have any questions related to this product just ask me down in the comments, I would be happy to help you with it. 
Have happy skin☺️✌🏻 #StayHome #StaySafe #Lockdown4 #dishagoyal .

1) Drinking green tea everyday can make your skin youthful.

4) Apart from removing toxins from the body, its anti-aging properties can help prevent fine lines and wrinkles too, making you look younger and healthier.

5) Its anti-bacterial properties fight against acne breakouts as well.

Add a cup of green tea in your daily routine and see the results. .

latestIgtvVideos.title: ✨ Gettin Glowy ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Quarantine has definitely been very healthy for my skin! Taking break from continuous shoots and taking care of my skin. “Today is a Glowy day ✨” Products I have used:
1) Choco caffeine glow face mask @mcaffeineofficial 
2) Calendula face mask sheet @thefaceshopindia_official 
3) Silver caffeine glow gel ( with aloevera gel) @mcaffeineofficial 
4) Calendula eye cream @thefaceshopindia_official 
5) Tender care @oriflameindia 
6) Lip&Cheek tint @thefaceshopindia_official 
Also as you guys know, My skin was facing severe acne and pigmentation issues since October last year; which made me so upset and sad. But all thanks to @drpankajchaturvedi_md @medlinksaesthetics 🙃

I have noticed a great change and improvement in my skin texture too♥️ Due the lockdown situation going on I have not been able to go for my sessions but as soon as the situation improves and my treatment ends, A full video of the treatment they have been given me since then would be up soon on my IGTV!☺️ Keep watching! 💋

#DishaGoyal #Quarantine
#QuarantineSkincare #Skincare #SkincareWithDG

latestIgtvVideos.title: Partner | Home-Workout 👩🏼‍🤝‍👩🏻
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
In our #QuarantineLife ,
we decided not to skip our workout sessions. 
Not only being #Quarantine and eating healthy would work; to immune ourselves, workout is very important. Home workout is not less effective  trust me! 
30-minutes of workout and we were red and sweaty like anything🙃 
We are preparing ourselves to #FightwithCorona 
#letsfighttogether .
.
.
Had an amazing “Leg & Core workout” yesterday with my partner @rashi___gupta 
Also I want to highlight one thing that working out with a partner is motivation to another level! There were some moments when I was heck exhausted and wanted to quit and @rashi___gupta pushed me a little and vice versa. I felt that was amazing especially when you are working out at home and you don’t have any trainer to push you😋 .
.
More Home workout sessions would be coming your way so Stay tuned!!
